Subject: [PATCH] Expose isolated MMC5 scope playback for host visualizers

---
 gme/Nsf_Emu.cpp | 113 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 gme/Nsf_Emu.h   |  11 +++++
 gme/gme.cpp     |  44 +++++++++++++++++++
 gme/gme.h       |  15 +++++++
 4 files changed, 183 insertions(+)

diff --git a/gme/Nsf_Emu.cpp b/gme/Nsf_Emu.cpp
